description: The team behind Tippy Toez Food Truck is using their tasteful talent to serve Indianapolis a delicious selection of massively scrumptious burgers, juicy bone-in chicken wings with an assortment of savory sauces, zesty pepper bombers, and so much more!Everything is made to order, so quickly take a trip to Tippy Toez Food Truck for some terrifically tasty all-American classics!
name: Tippy Toez Food Truck
